{"id":236239,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-河南访民刘炳同遭绑架关押期间儿子失踪/","date":"2012-07-01T10:46:09Z","modified":"2012-07-01T10:46:09Z","title":"维权网 | 河南访民刘炳同遭绑架关押期间儿子失踪（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-TM2YWqQRKwY/T_Ald1uhJlI/AAAAAAAAI2g/_0Jh7TmIRLk/s1600/%E5%88%98%E7%82%B3%E5%90%8C.JPG\"> </a></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-TM2YWqQRKwY/T_Ald1uhJlI/AAAAAAAAI2g/_0Jh7TmIRLk/s1600/%E5%88%98%E7%82%B3%E5%90%8C.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"239\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-TM2YWqQRKwY/T_Ald1uhJlI/AAAAAAAAI2g/_0Jh7TmIRLk/s320/%E5%88%98%E7%82%B3%E5%90%8C.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员关小令报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>，被从北京绑架回户籍地河南省郑州市管城区遭拘留关押至今的访民刘炳同，其儿子刘松也被失踪。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，上访被关押致残的访民刘炳同，一家人长期漂泊北京，妻子靠摆地摊赚钱维持生计。刘炳同到中央信访窗口登记时，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>，河南省地方政府和公安人员将刘炳同再次强行绑架回当地关进拘留所</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天后，又转往一处叫益民旅社囚禁至今。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘炳同的妻子说，政府经常连续数天不给他饭吃，还指使人殴打刘炳同。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民刘炳同被关押期间，其儿子刘松于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>失踪，至今下落不明，刘松的手机（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13621128354</span><span>）一直处于关机，政府还故意不释放刘炳同，刘炳同发出短信：由此想到我于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年被关花园村黑监狱时，管城区南关办事处书记对我说，你告我们了，黑社会会杀死我全家。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民刘炳同于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>发出短信说，看管我的人员说，管城区民政局赔给我一辆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>多元的轮椅，当时还带记者进行了拍录，我自己花</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4000</span><span>多元改造的电动残疾车，体积小，功率大，装有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>块电瓶，可行驶</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>多里路程，政府不是害人坑人吗？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>访民刘炳同因上访，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>岁的女儿失踪，现在儿子又失踪，他一家人希望得到社会各界的关注。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-2890873525316910156?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/90cd82a2B3E5908C.JPG-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[9085,19196]}